### Containerization
- Use multi-stage builds; final image must be distroless, non-root.
- Expose only UDP 5354; document protocol.
- Configure envs: `UPSTREAM_DNS`, `RATE_LIMIT_CAPACITY`, `RATE_LIMIT_REFILL`.

### Compose
- Limit memory; restart unless-stopped.
- Configure logging rotation.

